dmca.title: Blogger DMCA Complaint- Vogue
dmca.body:
Dear Sir or Madam: 

We represent The Conde Nast Publications, publisher of Vogue magazine.
 
It has come to our attention that a user of your website has posted, without permission, two (2) two-page photographic spreads from an as-yet unpublished issue of Vogue magazine, the January 2007 issue. The material can be found on the following url:

http://fadedyouth.blogspot.com, under the headings
dmca.principal_name: The Conde Nast Publications, Vogue Magazine
